title: How to end Zed's career (without Zhonyas)
body:
Hi. 
So I was playing urf and I actually ended up feeding early. At this point, Zed was like 10/0 and pretty unstoppable. Zed showed top so I went to shove mid, but he showed up sooner than I expected (I thought he would recall).
Last time people told me I did too much editing, so I held back a bit. Keep in mind my computer is not so great so the quality is not as good as I would like it to be.

Anyways, enjoy!

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NOcItgyv1h0
